    • Payroll

      public Payroll(int payrollID, Date payPeriodStartDate, Date payPeriodEndDate, float basicSalary, float overtimePay, float deductions, float netSalary, Employee emp)
      Constructs a Payroll object with specified parameters.
      Parameters:
      payrollID - Unique identifier for the payroll
      payPeriodStartDate - Start date of the pay period
      payPeriodEndDate - End date of the pay period
      basicSalary - Basic salary of the employee for the pay period
      overtimePay - Overtime pay for the pay period
      deductions - Deductions from the salary for the pay period
      netSalary - Net salary after deductions for the pay period
      emp - Associated employee for the payroll
